# FitLife PWA — Amy & Karl

## Deploy to Vercel in 5 steps

### Step 1 — Create GitHub repo
1. Go to github.com → New repository
2. Name it: `fitlife-app`
3. Keep it private
4. Click "Create repository"

### Step 2 — Upload these files
1. On your Mac, open Terminal
2. Run these commands:
```
cd ~/Downloads
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/fitlife-app
```
3. Copy all the files from this folder into the cloned repo folder
4. Then run:
```
cd fitlife-app
git add .
git commit -m "Initial deploy"
git push
```

### Step 3 — Deploy on Vercel
1. Go to vercel.com → Add New Project
2. Import your `fitlife-app` GitHub repo
3. Framework: Next.js (auto-detected)
4. Click Deploy

### Step 4 — Set up Vercel KV (database)
1. In your Vercel project → Storage tab
2. Click "Create Database" → KV
3. Name it `fitlife-kv`
4. Click Connect — Vercel auto-adds the env variables

### Step 5 — Add Anthropic API key
1. In Vercel project → Settings → Environment Variables
2. Add: `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` = your API key from console.anthropic.com
3. Redeploy (Settings → Deployments → Redeploy)

### Your app URLs will be:
- Home: `https://fitlife-app.vercel.app/`
- Amy's Challenge: `https://fitlife-app.vercel.app/amy`
- Karl's Challenge: `https://fitlife-app.vercel.app/karl`

### Add to phone home screen:
**iPhone:** Open in Safari → Share button → "Add to Home Screen"
**Android:** Open in Chrome → 3-dot menu → "Add to Home Screen"

Both phones should use `https://fitlife-app.vercel.app/` as the shortcut.
The app opens full screen like a native app.

## Need to update Karl's challenge?
1. Edit `src/pages/karl.js` — update the CHALLENGE_DATA import or add custom data
2. `git add . && git commit -m "Update Karl challenge" && git push`
3. Vercel auto-redeploys in ~30 seconds

## Project structure
```
src/
  pages/
    index.js      ← Home dashboard (/, /home)
    amy.js        ← Amy's challenge (/amy)
    karl.js       ← Karl's challenge (/karl)
    api/
      data.js     ← API: read/write shared data
      ai.js       ← API: Coach + horoscope AI
  data/
    index.js      ← All workout, food, music data
  hooks/
    useData.js    ← Shared data fetching hook
  lib/
    storage.js    ← Vercel KV database helper
  styles/
    globals.css   ← Global styles
```
